{"tid":1411393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"零售罷工未？？！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:35:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T05:43:39.000Z","uid":44663,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"71187a2dc3012c903264d9ddbcc782133f59d79a","tid":1411393,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:35:56.000Z","msg":"大家係2個月黎都見過好多公司被媒體圍攻，然後杯葛<br />\n零售公司除左賺錢，最在意就係企業形象<br />\n上次新界西宵禁事件，都係美資化妝品公司帶頭做起<br />\n呢班公司唔表達政治立場係因為唔敢得罪任何一方 <br />\n公司心態是企後一步，雨過天清後就又可以食兩家茶飯<br />\n作為前零售中級前線管理層<br />\n做得呢行員工唔係怕罷工，只驚無勤工<br />\n全部老細都係紅底做大陸人生意<br />\n<br />\n我地要做既係牽一髮動全身，一定係連鎖零售行先<br />\n外資化妝品（shiseido、dior、YSL、SKII etc...）、莎莎、卓悅、Colormix、萬寧、屈臣氏、BODY SHOP.......<br />\n太多緊有一間係附近<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">特別好多係擺明做大陸人生意，係咁意係住宅區開幾間扮重視本地人果ｄ<br />\n不過唔係重點</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今次活動唔洗好多人，每間舖３-4個都夠<br />\n要做既當然和理非啦，特別商埸舖<br />\n係舖前和平地舉起標語<br />\n例如： 此公司支持林鄭 香港加油<br />\n都係果句<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公司除左賺錢外，最在意就係企業形象（特別外資）</span></span><br />\n分分鐘有藍絲和應tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重要可以響應埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工唔好幫襯非罷工公司</span></span><br />\n今日咁得閒，仲唔出街支持下商戶？<br />\n想支拎埋連鎖餐廳當然無任歡迎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我有假放，我都想多ｄ人有假放<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/bc6/e9f/bc6e9f39d52e7de9f32bfe1d7a08cdfbae0959c6_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fbc6%2Fe9f%2Fbc6e9f39d52e7de9f32bfe1d7a08cdfbae0959c6_n.jpg&h=1c0cb196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n導讀<br />\n我是大型外資零售企業的前線管理層。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403014</a>"},{"pid":"040791a75eed2ac2c7ef8d7e0e5514c4f720761c","tid":1411393,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:37:14.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"f91e5d4710487c0ccf4446fddd9250fc3642b6ab","tid":1411393,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:37:29.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2d6c5c6c71ebf7547e01db3bb5be1d7a18a0b63d","tid":1411393,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:37:43.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"340e756c1d36f745a3f09f1580460fb1e4e00f9e","tid":1411393,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:37:55.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"8c7a280eca79a8b14b57de2c8442b9306c2a94ce","tid":1411393,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:38:07.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"8d8cb58191d947499bb03e8d0ef3a283ccb253d6","tid":1411393,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:38:26.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"d061f93ed02a0c0be9f9e21e64c823a456746a0d","tid":1411393,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:38:26.000Z","msg":"係佢舖頭門口掟下TG, 唔罷工都唔得啦"},{"pid":"e1beff32f5f5e4039de3dd43f9e3d3f269bbdb78","tid":1411393,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:38:41.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"695ca7bc6f80e5e288d2b5c42873d40c36073d7e","tid":1411393,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:38:51.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"a8cc8a16a8fff889a4ea544727ea9a2e8802f16b","tid":1411393,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:38:55.000Z","msg":"好多集會地方附近都有商場<br />\n覺得熱就去嘆下冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5dc68bafb00c6a3f30ad7a391be05316db3caf","tid":1411393,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4701f2e43b56f036d806aba3ad315ff8963fc43e","tid":1411393,"uid":44663,"li